bourer occurs due to substance abuse or suicide.", "003-normal": "Source / Reference Link: https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/raipur/chhattisgarh-ahead-of-rural-polls-cm-sop-for-labourers-of-unorganised-sector/articleshow/73065287.cms"}}